name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Voicenotes AI: Transcribe Notes and Meetings

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Voicenotes is an intelligent note-taker that let's you transcribe voice notes and meetings in 100+ languages.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Voicenotes AI Notes & Meetings is the ultimate tool for professionals, students, and anyone needing to capture and transcribe audio directly from their browser. Whether you're attending virtual meetings, lectures, or just need to record voice notes, Voicenotes AI Notes & Meetings offers a seamless, high-quality audio recording solution directly within Chrome.
